title: Arizona State holds on late, upsets No. 7 UCLA 38-23
text:
> Top News Arizona State holds on late, upsets No. 7 UCLA 38-23 Arizona State wide receiver Ryan Jenkins, right, can't hold on to a pass while being defended by UCLA defensive lineman Sam Tai during the first half of an NCAA college football game, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Pasadena, Calif. (AP Photo/Mark J. Terrill)
